A cyberpunk cityscape at night viewed from above, showing countless parallel data streams flowing like neon rivers through dark urban canyons, each stream a different electric color - cyan, magenta, green - representing asynchronous processes running simultaneously. The streams branch, merge, and flow around massive dark monolithic server towers that pulse with subtle internal light. Some streams complete their journey in bright bursts of energy while others fade into shadow, visualizing success and failure states. The atmosphere is humid with digital fog, rain catching the glow of the data rivers below. No human figures, just the abstract beauty of parallel computation rendered as an living urban nervous system.
